Assignment - 
There are two parts to this assignment.
The first is to test your ability to code out designs in html and css.
The second part is animating texts and backgrounds to help the AI create videos. 

Part - 1
This part is to check your ability to transform designs into code. This will be a simple landing page design. You will be marked on the following - 
The structure and cleanliness of your code (both html and css) 
Your attention to detail (how close can you get your code to the design)

Please find the design and the related assets in this link - 

https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1mAHa7ZHvK6RaOPWC_d3H_GK2X-6_083D?usp=sharing

Bonus: If you can get the colors exactly and make it responsive.



